#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:85
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_PORTAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You reach the beacon where the strange anomalous energy spike was detected, but strangely, you don't find anything. You consider jumping away but suddenly what looks like a portal with a deep blue tint appears in an empty patch of space nearby. It seems to be barely large enough for your ship to pass through.\n"
"\n"
"\tAenwithe looks at the portal in pure amazement. \"This energy... I haven't felt anything like it since... Captain, we must investigate this! The Paragon can wait. This is much, much more important.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:90
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_PORTAL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Enter."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:92
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_PORTAL\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Going through the portal is a big enough challenge by itself, but things "
"become more complicated as the portal begins collapsing on itself while "
"you're halfway through. You divert as much power as possible to your engines"
" and somehow manage to get through it as everything goes dark. The only "
"thing left to do is to press forward..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:99
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_PORTAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "We have more important things to do than wander into random portals."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:101
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_PORTAL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"At the end of the day, the Paragon is still your priority, and whatever is "
"behind that portal might require more time than it's worth."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:103
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_PORTAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:107
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_PORTAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:141
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr ""
"The location of the repair center that might be able to repair your broken "
"crew."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:142
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "Explored location. Nothing left of interest."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:143
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER\"]/beaconType/undiscoveredTooltip"
msgstr "An unvisited location."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:145
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You finally arrive at the repair center. Perhaps you can finally fix the "
"Obelisk corpse that you have been carrying around for your whole journey."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:148
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:150
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You are suddenly hailed by the repair center. A Commonwealth Obelisk appears on your screen, speaking frantically, \"Outsider! I would never have guessed that I would be happy to see you, but we have a major crisis on our hands and we desperately need your help.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\"You see, we were upgrading our auto cruiser to be better equipped to fight against the Exterminators should they ever breach our defenses, but we accidentally made a typo in its aggression level and now it's out for blood. If you can wear down its hull enough for us to shut it down, that would be great, but if that's not an option then you may destroy the ship if necessary. Just help us and we will happily return the favor!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:156
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Help them out and attack the vessel."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:158
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The auto's message blares over your speakers, \"WARNING, EXTERMINATOR LEVEL "
"THREAT DETECTED! COUNTERMEASURES INITIATED!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:161
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:167
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "We can't afford to take that thing on, sorry."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:169
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You apologise to them again before shutting off the call and preparing to "
"jump."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:171
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
