#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:236
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER_SURRENDER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The auto is struggling to keep up with your barrage. The Commonwealths hail "
"you. \"Excellent job! Hold on for another minute while our engineers work on"
" disabling the ship, and we can finally stop this whole blunder!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:240
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER_SURRENDER\"]/triggeredEvent/triggeredEventBox/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"The engineers need more time to shut down the Auto. Hold on for just a "
"little bit longer!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:247
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_AUTO_CRUISER_SUCCESS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You've managed to hold out just long enough. Eventually, the Auto-ship shuts"
" down, its many lights going dark for now."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:252
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_AUTO_CRUISER_SUCCESS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:254
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_AUTO_CRUISER_SUCCESS\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealths hail you. \"Excellent job, Outsider! Your combat prowess "
"is nothing to scoff at. As promised, we will not only be at your service, "
"but we'll also offer you the blueprints of the cruiser you stopped; it's the"
" least we can do.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:258
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_AUTO_CRUISER_SUCCESS\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"FR_COMMONWEALTHS_BODY\"]/text"
msgstr "(Commonwealth's Body) Show them the broken body."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:260
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_AUTO_CRUISER_SUCCESS\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"FR_COMMONWEALTHS_BODY\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealths examine the body from top to bottom, their 'eyes' widening when they realize who the corpse is from. They talk among each other for a while and then they bring it inside the facility and ask you to wait in your ship until they are done. It takes a while but they eventually return with the Commonwealth fully repaired.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\"Savior! I can't tell you how grateful I am for you to have gone through all of that trouble just for little old me. It will be an honor to serve you aboard your ship! My name is Bellrennis, but you can call my Daisy. I'm the Commonwealth's Lead Explorer! I have been deactived for oh so long... But now I get to see the outside world again, and hopefully this time not get blown to pieces by the Exterminators.\"\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tDaisy turns to you and 'smiles', already on her way to the cockpit. \"What are we waiting for? Let's get going!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:267
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_AUTO_CRUISER_SUCCESS\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"FR_COMMONWEALTHS_BODY\"]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Daisy"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:269
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_AUTO_CRUISER_SUCCESS\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"FR_COMMONWEALTHS_BODY\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:275
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_AUTO_CRUISER_SUCCESS\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "We wouldn't be against some resources."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:277
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_AUTO_CRUISER_SUCCESS\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealths nod before sending you a crate filled with supplies, as "
"well as fully repairing your hull. You bid them farewell and prepare to "
"jump."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:281
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_AUTO_CRUISER_SUCCESS\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

