msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:297
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER_DESTROYED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Auto-ship doesn't seem to be able to resist its damage anymore. Its hull"
" cracks in half before the ship explodes, only debris being left."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:300
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER_DESTROYED\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:302
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER_DESTROYED\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealths are relieved but sad at the same time. They hail you, "
"their voices clearly deflated. \"I understand that you had no other choice; "
"still, I'm sad we couldn't save the ship. However, you did help us, and for "
"that you have our thanks. Now, do you need help with anything?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:304
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_REPAIR_CENTER_DESTROYED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"FR_COMMONWEALTHS_BODY\"]/text"
