#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:367
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "The location of the Exit Portal from this sector."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:368
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "Explored location. Location of the Exit Portal."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:370
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You have arrived at the location of what you assume is the rift. Sure "
"enough, the rift is there, but it seems to be heavily protected by the "
"biggest ship you have seen so far, a heavily armed Dreadnought-class "
"Commonwealth cruiser."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:375
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:377
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You attempt to hail the massive ship, and to your surprise, whoever is in "
"charge responds to your hails. \"Outsider, if you value your life then we "
"suggest you back off. You cannot leave the sector under any circumstances - "
"no one can.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:379
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "We aren't backing off; fight the Dreadnought!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:381
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You power up your weapons and move in to destroy the ship. Its blue lights "
"shine with power and its frightful artillery powers up as well."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:384
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:394
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT_AI\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"All of the crew aboard the Dreadnought are dead, but the ship keeps "
"fighting. There must be some sort of AI mode attached to it!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:397
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT_AI\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "We have to keep fighting!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:403
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You watch the massive ship crack in half before exploding into "
"unrecognizably small pieces. You collect what you can from the debris."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:416
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:418
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT_WIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You decide to take the time to make sure your systems and crew are all in good shape before jumping. You have the strange feeling this isn't over yet...\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t(Press the jump button to continue.)"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:428
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT_JUMP\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You make sure everyone is ready before you start the delicate process of "
"exiting through the portal. It's a bit bigger than the last one, and it "
"doesn't seem to start collapsing midway through either, making the final "
"moment way less stressful."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:430
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT_JUMP\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:432
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_RIFT_JUMP\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Eventually you fully exit through the other side of the rift. You gaze back and think over the strange adventure you just had, a melancholy hitting you as you realize that you won't ever be able to go back there, and any friends you made won't ever see you again. \n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tSuddenly, the mood completely shifts as your ship is forcefully stopped midway through the sector jump. Wherever you are right now will have to be your new landing site unless you want to risk being torn apart mid-jump."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:463
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_STORE_HOSTILE_COMMONWEALTH_AUTO\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"A nearby Commonwealth merchant appears to be currently under attack from an "
"Auto-ship. If you help them, they might be willing to trade with you."

