"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_COGNITIVE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"FR_LIST_MEDICAL_NONBALLISTIC\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Medical Non-Ballistic Weapons) Use your medical weapon to repair them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1047
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_COGNITIVE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"FR_LIST_MEDICAL_NONBALLISTIC\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"With your Non-Ballistic Medical weapon you are able to repair the Proto-"
"Cognitive much faster than expected. Surprisingly, they seem to be more "
"skilled than any other Proto-Cognitive that you have seen so far! They thank"
" you and offer to join your crew."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1050
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_COGNITIVE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"FR_LIST_MEDICAL_NONBALLISTIC\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1054
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_COGNITIVE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"FR_LIST_MEDICAL_NONBALLISTIC\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1060
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_COGNITIVE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"clonebay\"]/text"
msgstr "(Clone Bay) Register the Cognitive and clone them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1062
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_COGNITIVE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"clonebay\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems you acted just in time, as the Cognitive's faulty electronics were "
"just about to give up. Upon cloning them you notice that, surprisingly, they"
" seem to be more skilled than any other Proto-Cognitive that you have seen "
"so far! They thank you and offer to join your crew."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1065
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_COGNITIVE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"clonebay\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1069
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_COGNITIVE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"clonebay\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1075
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_COGNITIVE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[12]/text"
msgstr "There is nothing we can do."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1077
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_COGNITIVE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[12]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"With no other choice, all you can do is watch as the Cognitive gradually "
"shuts down for good. You release them back into the void."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1079
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_COGNITIVE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[12]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1083
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_COGNITIVE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[12]/event/choice[2]/text"
