msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_COGNITIVE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1108
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"An agitated Commonwealth hails you. \"You, Outsider. We know what your plan "
"is. You wish to leave the sector, correct? In that case, I wish to help you "
"by donating one of my personal drones to your cause.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1110
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"-999\"]/text"
msgstr "Accept."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1112
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"-999\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealth gives you the schematics. To your surprise, it's a Royal "
"drone!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1117
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "Accept."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1119
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealth gives you the schematics. To your surprise, it's not a "
"Commonwealth drone, but a regular ancient drone."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1124
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/text"
msgstr "Accept."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1126
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealth goes silent for a little while. You patiently wait for your"
" drone when you are suddenly startled by your boarder detection alarms! It "
"seems your \"drone\" has arrived."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1131
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Reject their offer."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1133
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealth is confused why you would refuse their help. Still, they "
"understand and leave you alone."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1135
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1139
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1147
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_AUGMENT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"A group of Commonwealths hails you. \"Outsider, we are testing a highly "
"experimental augment system which we hope could help in our future fight "
"against the Exterminators. Would you care to test it out?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1149
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_AUGMENT\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"-999\"]/text"
msgstr "Accept."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1151
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_AUGMENT\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"-999\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealths work on your ship for hours, but eventually they finish. "
"When you ask what they did, they simply smile and point to your internal "
"augment list, where it shows a brand new augment has been installed - a Pre-"
"Igniter!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1156
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_AUGMENT\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"-1\"]/text"
msgstr "Accept."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1158
