#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1186
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"A Commonwealth Auto hails you. \"HO HO HO OUTSIDER. DO YOU WISH FOR: A "
"HOLIDAY GIFT?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1188
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"-999\"]/text"
msgstr "We do!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1190
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"-999\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Auto plays some kind of holiday song over the radio and sends a large "
"crate full of supplies."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1195
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "We do!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1197
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Auto plays some kind of holiday song over the radio and sends a medium "
"crate of supplies."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1202
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/text"
msgstr "We do!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1204
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Auto plays some kind of holiday song over the radio; however, it seems "
"distorted and slowed down. Suddenly a strange present is beamed over. You "
"send your crew to open it but a huge explosion shakes your ship as they open"
" it - it was a bomb! By now the Auto has already jumped away so there's "
"nothing you can do about it."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1208
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"The blown-up crew member stumbles out of the clone bay. \"I will never see "
"Renegade Day the same way again...\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1213
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "No thank you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1215
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Auto's tone seems noticeably less enthusiastic. Still, they thank you "
"for your time and jump away."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1217
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1221
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ITEM_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1246
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As you jump into the beacon, your feed is filled with warning messages "
"coming from the nearby prison planet. \"WARNING! WARNING! PLANET ON "
"LOCKDOWN! A PRISONER IS ATTEMPTING TO ESCAPE!\" The message loops endlessly."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1248
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Dock."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1250
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Just as you are about to enter the atmosphere of the planet, you are stopped"
" by a strange Commonwealth ship with pink lights. An Obelisk cloaked in a "
"drape hails you, but their pink lights betray their \"perfect\" disguise. "
"\"Mortal- I mean, 'Outsider', please help me! I'm being chased by these "
"useless beings- I mean, misguided souls who think I'm a Royal! An "
"understandable mistake since I'm more perfect than them, but alas, I'm "
"simply a lowly and worthless little commontrasher- I mean Commonwealther. "
"Please kill these guards chasing me!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1252
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "This guy is obviously an Exterminator, don't let them escape!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1254
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The \"Commonwealth\" snarls and drops their disguise. \"You little mortal "
"rat! I will make you kneel and then end this cursed infection once and for "
"all! For Her Majesty, Queen Y!\" Their weapons come online as the ship "
"charges towards you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1257
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1263
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Attack the guard and help the escapee"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1265
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The guard is taken by surprise as you attack their ship. Still they won't "
"back down from a fight."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1268
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1276
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Stay away."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1278
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You'd rather not get involved with Commonwealth fugitives. The planet should"
" be able to handle the situation without your help."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1280
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1284
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1293
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL_GUARD_KILL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You are hailed by the escapee. \"Well, would you look at that. I guess "
"mortals aren't as useless as I thought. Since I'm being unfairly chased and "
"persecuted at the moment, I will take refuge in your ship for the time "
"being. Please don't embarrass me while I'm aboard.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1299
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ROYAL_ESCAPEE_KILL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You are hailed by the guard. \"Thank the stars you stopped them, Outsider! "
"We are forever in your debt from this day onwards! If that Exterminator "
"managed to leave the sector... Well, let's just be happy they failed. All "
"thanks to you, meaning you deserve a reward worthy of the danger you "
"stopped. We avoid giving these out since we know the damage that these "
"horrific weapons can inflict, but I believe you have earned the right to use"
" them. Peace be with you, Outsider.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1306
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You hail a Commonwealth ship studying the nearby star constellation. "
"\"Outsider, please don't distract us! We are in the middle of a very "
"important task at the moment. Peace be with you.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1309
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the surveyors."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1311
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The surveyors are taken by surprise, one of your shots nearly hitting them "
"before they can even react. They turn their weapons on and advance towards "
"you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1314
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1320
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave them alone."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1322
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The team appreciates your consideration and decides to give you a small box "
"of scrap as thanks."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1325
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1329
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1335
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[@req=\"ADV_SCANNERS\"]/text"
msgstr "(Long-Ranged Scanners) Offer them your detailed map data."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1337
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_GENERIC\"]/choice[@req=\"ADV_SCANNERS\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealth's interest is very much piqued. \"Outsider, that data is "
"incredible! We haven't seen the outside realms in so long... Please, accept "
"our gratitude and compensation.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1345
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find a Commonwealth Auto repairing itself nearby. It seems the asteroid "
"field wasn't kind to the small Auto."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1351
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the Auto."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1353
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Auto doesn't attempt to fight; instead, it immediately attempts to flee."
" If it manages to escape, it will certainly tell others of your actions."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1356
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1362
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "ignore the auto and scrap the nearby field."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1364
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You decide to ignore the Auto. Instead, you scrap some of the broken off "
"bits that are floating around from the Auto. It isn't much, but every little"
" bit helps."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1367
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1371
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1377
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_REPAIR_ALL\"]/text"
msgstr "(Repair Drone) Fix the auto ship. [1|]"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1379
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_REPAIR_ALL\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your repair drone quickly patches up the Auto-ship. Once fixed, it "
"distributes supplies and patches up your hull. \"OUTSIDER. APPRECIATION: "
"ETERNAL. PLEASE HAVE: REPAIR + REWARD + FAME\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1389
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGINEER\"]/text"
msgstr "(Engineer Crew) Fix the auto ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1391
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGINEER\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your Engineer tries to explain that they're only used to working on Rebel "
"Auto-ships, but you convince them to try anyways. They manage to get the "
"drone working long enough to repair some hull before something goes wrong "
"and the ship explodes! Luckily you weren't caught in the blast zone, but "
"still, with a heavy heart you scrap what you can out of the ship's remains."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1398
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGI\"]/text"
msgstr "(Engi Crew) Fix the auto ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1400
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGI\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your Engi is no stranger to working on Auto-ships and drones, though they've"
" never had to repair anything quite like this ship. Surprisingly, they "
"manage to repair the Auto-ship. Once fixed, it distributes supplies and "
"patches up your hull. \"OUTSIDER. APPRECIATION: ETERNAL. PLEASE HAVE: REPAIR"
" + REWARD + FAME\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1407
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_commonwealth\"]/text"
msgstr "(Commonwealth Crew) Fix the auto ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1409
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_AUTO\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_commonwealth\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your Commonwealth is no stranger to working on Auto-ships and drones; in "
"fact, repairing broken guardian ships is just part of the routine for them. "
"Unsurprisingly, they manage to repair the Auto-ship. Once fixed it "
"distributes supplies and patches up your hull. \"OUTSIDER. APPRECIATION: "
"ETERNAL. PLEASE HAVE: REPAIR + REWARD + FAME\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1418
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_AUTO_ESCAPE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Auto escapes before you can stop it. It will surely broadcast your "
"attempted murder to every living being in the tri-star area. Oh well..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1423
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As you are exploring the asteroid field, you notice a Commonwealth ship "
"somewhat far from the beacon. Its shields are down and its hull is being "
"constantly pelted by asteroids. At this rate they won't last much longer."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1428
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_DEFENSE\"]/text"
msgstr "(Defense Drone) Use a Defense Drone to protect their ship. [-1|]"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1432
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_OVERCHARGER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Overcharger Drone) Use an Overcharger Drone to protect their ship. [-1|]"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1436
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_REPAIR_CREW\"]/text"
msgstr "(Repair Drone) Send a Repair Drone to fix their Shields. [-1|]"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1440
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE\"]/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_BOMB_REPAIR\"]/text"
msgstr "(Repair Cluster) Launch a repair bomb into their Shields. [-1|]"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1444
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE\"]/choice[@req=\"teleporter\"]/text"
msgstr "(Teleporter) Offer to beam them aboard your ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1448
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE\"]/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_ARMOR\"]/text"
msgstr "(Hull Armor) Shield their ship with yours and escort them out."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1452
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE\"]/choice[@req=\"COMBAT_REPAIR\"]/text"
msgstr "(Repair-Bot Dispersal) Repair their shields with the nanobots."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1456
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE\"]/choice[8]/text"
msgstr "Attack the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1458
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE\"]/choice[8]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Though severely damaged by the asteroid field, the enemy doesn't back down "
"from a fight."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1461
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE\"]/choice[8]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1467
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE\"]/choice[9]/text"
msgstr "Stay back and don't get involved."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1469
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE\"]/choice[9]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"This asteroid storm is too severe for you to risk saving a ship of "
"strangers. You can jump away now, or you can try and collect some of the "
"scrap from the distressed ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1471
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE\"]/choice[9]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Don't risk it."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1475
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE\"]/choice[9]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Try and scoop up some scrap."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1483
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE_SUCCESS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your idea works perfectly, and within minutes the Commonwealth's shields are"
" back in fully working order. They hail you. \"Thank you so much for your "
"help, Outsider. I always believed in the kindness of strangers, and it warms"
" my mechanical heart to know I was right. Please, take this weapon: it's the"
" least I could do.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1490
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//eventList[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE_TELEPORT\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"You manage to teleport the Commonwealth onto your ship just in time, as "
"their ship is reduced to nothing but a pile of scrap. The Commonwealth looks"
" far from pleased about losing their ship, but they are still grateful to "
"you for saving their life and decide to serve on your ship from now on."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1494
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//eventList[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE_TELEPORT\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"You manage to teleport the one of the Cognitives onto your ship just in "
"time, as their ship is reduced to nothing but a pile of scrap. The Cognitive"
" begins to examine the situation and decides that serving you is its best "
"chance for survival."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1501
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//eventList[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE_GREEDY\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"You manage to salvage some of the scrap. However, a few asteroids sneak "
"through your defenses, leaving you with a few holes in your ship to deal "
"with."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1510
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//eventList[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE_GREEDY\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"You manage to salvage all of the scrap around the ship, though you end up "
"taking so long that you witness the Commonwealth ship succumbing to its "
"damage and exploding. Oh well, more stuff to collect."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1514
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//eventList[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_ASTEROIDS_RESCUE_GREEDY\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"Before you can even try to collect the scrap, an asteroid flies right "
"through your defenses and critically damages your shields. You pull away and"
" charge your FTL drive before things get worse."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1524
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find a Commonwealth ship waiting for you near a pulsar. As soon as you "
"spot them, they hail you. \"Outsider! We have been waiting for your arrival."
" We forsee that you will soon fight the dreadful dreadnought guarding the "
"one and only exit to this place. The dreadnought is no ordinary foe, for its"
" artillery is highly ionized. If you aren't well prepared, then it will "
"disable your shields and weapons, leaving you defenseless and unarmed.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1528
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1530
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"To make sure you are well equipped for that mission, we want to test your "
"prowess in battle when your systems are overloaded with ionic energy. For "
"that, we will temporarily give you a special piece of technology that will "
"nullify your anti-ion defenses for the battle. Win, and you may keep this "
"technology for your own use. What do you say, Outsider?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1532
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Deal, bring it on!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1534
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealth smiles proudly. They beam their augment into your cargo and"
" wait for you to install them. Once your preparations are ready, they turn "
"their weapons online and advance."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1539
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1545
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Refuse the test."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1547
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealth is very disappointed, but they allow you to leave "
"regardless."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1549
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1553
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1563
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_SHIP_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST_SURRENDER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The tester hails you. \"That was a excellent display of skill and "
"experience, Outsider! Consider the test over now. Power down your weapons so"
" we can remove the augment and give you your prize!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1565
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_SHIP_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST_SURRENDER\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Power down your weapons."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1567
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_SHIP_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST_SURRENDER\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealth does the same and then waits for you to uninstall the test "
"augment before beaming it back to their ship. Your reward arrives shortly "
"after - an aether-based augment that completely removes enemy ion "
"resistance!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1574
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_SHIP_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST_SURRENDER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1580
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_SHIP_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST_SURRENDER\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Ignore them and continue fighting."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1586
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST_KILL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"With a heavy heart, you remove the test augment. If only things had gone "
"differently..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1593
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST_BAIL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Outsider, do you wish to stop the test? You may remove the augment, but "
"our fight will end.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1595
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST_BAIL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "No, we will keep fighting!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1600
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST_BAIL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "We do, stop the test!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1602
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST_BAIL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealth is very disappointed but they allow you to leave "
"regardless."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1607
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST_BAIL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1611
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_TEST_BAIL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1619
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_AUTO\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find a Commonwealth Auto close to the pulsar, acting erratically. The "
"Auto hails you and sends a bunch of garbled messages that make no sense at "
"all. It doesn't seem aggressive, however."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1623
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_AUTO\"]/choice[@req=\"ION_ARMOR\"]/text"
msgstr "(Partial Ion Immunity) Shield their ship from the next pulsar pulse."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1627
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_AUTO\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_full_ion_immunity\"]/text"
msgstr "(Full Ion Immunity) Shield their ship from the next pulsar pulse."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1631
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_AUTO\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Attack the Auto."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1633
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_AUTO\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Auto-ship lets out a horrifying screech over your comms and then moves "
"to attack."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1636
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_AUTO\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1642
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_AUTO\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Leave it alive."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1644
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_AUTO\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr "You slowly back away from the Auto and get ready to jump away."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1646
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_AUTO\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1650
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_AUTO\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1658
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_AUTO_PARTIAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your plan... kind of works? The ship isn't hit by the full ionic blast, but "
"the little amount it absorbed was still enough to overload its reactor and "
"cause it to explode. A shame, but at least you can salvage its remains."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1664
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_PULSAR_AUTO_FULL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your ion defenses are more than enough to fully absorb the next ion blast, "
"allowing the Auto to get the chance to fully purge all the ionic energy from"
" its system. Once it's back in working order, it hails you. \"OUTSIDER. "
"APPRECIATION: ETERNAL. PLEASE HAVE: REWARD + FAME\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1670
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_SOLAR_STATION\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It's strange to find an station so close to a star, but perhaps aether-based"
" stations are more resistant to solar flares? Either way, they hail you. "
"\"Outsider, we don't advise you to stay this close to this star, or any "
"stars for that matter. Your hull can't take the punishment necessary to "
"survive these dangerous solar flares. I suggest you leave before your hull "
"becomes too damaged.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1673
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_SOLAR_STATION\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Is there anything we can do to help?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1675
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_SOLAR_STATION\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealth is surprised by your question, which they think about for a"
" moment. \"We did lose a research probe near the star. We were studying the "
"star's internal activities when an unusually strong flare blew it off-course"
" and damaged its navigation systems. Normally, it would be able to repair "
"itself automatically, but the flare also damaged its maintenance systems, "
"preventing it from automatically repairing its piloting. However, its "
"emergency repair systems should still be online from what little info we "
"could gather. If you can trigger those systems by attacking it, the probe "
"should be able to repair its piloting system and jump to somewhere safe "
"enough for us to repair it fully. What do you say?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1677
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_SOLAR_STATION\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
