"obscure room in the vault. Searching further, your crew finds a Royal drone "
"and, at the center of the room, a Hyper-Igniter! From the transcripts and "
"maps lying around, it seems that the Commonwealth hoped to use it against "
"the Royals but were prevented from doing so. Your crew return triumphantly "
"with a great haul."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml:1961
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_commonwealth.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_COMMONWEALTH_STORM_AUTO\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find a Commonwealth Auto-ship drifting through the storm, its systems "
"barely online. It attempts to hail you but it seems that it used too much "
"power in doing so, causing it to shut down. A few minutes later, it manages "
"to turn itself back online, but it seems the shut down has damaged its power"
" supply."

